extends navbars.pug

block content	

	#aboutus.container
		h5.text-center Band Biography
		.container
			.row.justify-content-center
				img.aboutuspic(src='../static/css/images/logos/vango.png')
			.row.justify-content-center.bio
				p
					span
						| We are 
						span.yesdevil YES DEVIL
					|  , a hard rock band based out of the San Francisco Bay Area. Our sound is shaped by a wide range of influences from a variety of genres. From the bluesy origins of rock 'n' roll to in your face heavy metal, we have a modern take on the classic sounds that have shaped rock music into what it is today. After releasing our first EP, 
					a(href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/get-damned-ep/924263735", target='_blank') Get Damned
					| , under our original band name and line-up (Se7en Dead), a series of break-ups and line-up changes prompted us to rebrand ourselves a handful of times before finally re-emerging as Yes Devil. With our new full length album, 
					a(href="/music") The High Cost of Living Low
					| , we tie together years of experiences we've shared together as a band. These songs embody the essence of these experiences, the lives we've lived, the people we've met, and lessons we've learned. 
			.members
				h5 -Members-
				.logan.row.justify-content-center
					div
						img(src='../static/css/images/aboutus/loganbio.jpg')
